        [
          "Traveling musician to wanders from town to town gatherin gthe stories, and you've heard LA has some strange stories.",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "Jenn Wolfe"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You took up traveling and playing from city-to-city as a teenager, shaking the dusty off your feet. You played one dusty, dank bar and club after another, and as you went along, you gathered stories of all sorts; happy, sad, tragic, whatever, you collected them and turned them into the stories and songs you performed. Someone apparently liked your story, because they decided to keep you doing it forever. Since that night, you've wandered the length and breadth of the country, doing the same every night that you have for decades. You prefer Camarilla cities, they seem to be the most easy to live at as long as you promise to behave yourself, but the Anarchs can be okay as well. You've seen everything there is to be seen in the country, and it's been a while since you've been to LA. You've been hearing crazy stories from there, and you are curious. Go check it out and see what's going on there.\n\nYou know life is dangerous for Gangrels, they have been in and out of the Camarilla and few princes have welcomed them in large numbers. You know from your stories something big is coming, strange events are happening; hunters, elders disappearing, and strange happenings that seem straight out of myth and legend. Maybe finding someplace safe to hunker down for whatever is coming won't be so bad, and maybe LA can be that place."
        ],
